@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> OnHold
OnHold --> Delivered : update
Delivered --> Archived : submit
Archived --> Shipped : submit
Shipped --> Pending : process
Pending --> Closed : submit
Pending : entry / log follower
OnHold --> Pending : revert
Closed --> [*]
@enduml